<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>9 SPEED AND 11 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTO-1X707LL/DLL/MLL AND RTO-1X709MLL MODELS - REMOVE - AUXILIARY
        DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="3">
        <title>AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY</title>
        <para>Before removing the auxiliary drive gear, the auxiliary section must be removed.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the mainshaft rear groove snap ring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302034">Figure 34</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302034" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302034" filename="../figg13/G1302034.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 34. Auxiliary Drive Gear Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the auxiliary bearing retainer ring bolts (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302034">Figure 34</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Insert three (3) of the bolts in the specially tapped holes of the retainer ring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302035">Figure 35</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302035" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302035" filename="../figg13/G1302035.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 35. Bolts In Retainer Ring</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten the bolts evenly to force the auxiliary drive gear assembly from the case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302035">Figure 35</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the auxiliary drive gear from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302036">Figure 36</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1302036" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1302036" filename="../figg13/G1302036.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 36. Auxiliary Drive Gear</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the mainshaft snap ring.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
